-- Everton Sells Fellaini to Manchester United for $42.7 Million
-- B y   D a n   B a y n e s
-- 2013-09-02T23:05:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-09-02/everton-sells-fellaini-to-manchester-united-for-42-7-million.html
Everton said it sold midfielder
Marouane Fellaini to English Premier League soccer rival
 Manchester United  for 27.5 million pounds ($42.7 million).  Everton said on its  website  late yesterday that it also
sold striker Victor Anichebe to West Bromwich Albion for as much
as 6 million pounds.  The Toffees paid Wigan 13 million pounds to sign midfielder
James McCarthy on a long-term contract and took Chelsea striker
Romelu Lukaku and Manchester City midfielder Gareth Barry on
season-long loans.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Baynes at 
 dbaynes@bloomberg.net  